Has a lot of potential! The growing system is great for teaching those new 
to growing! Here's my problem: you can't choose where you trim very 
effectively. You get the option of trimming the top, or the lowest 
branches. But when the leaves start yellowing near the bottom of the plant, 
clicking on the "trim bottom" button doesn't trim those branches; it trims 
the healthy branches and leaves AROUND the yellowed leaves. Please fix this 
huge blemish on an otherwise phenomenal simulator
replyContent: Thanks for your feedback. Currently the scissors trims top and bottom of plant.  It serves the two main cuts, top to create multiple tips, and bottom to remove branches furthest from light and focus plants energy on more useful limbs. We are working on a more advanced trimming tool with more options.

content:
Happy to see it arrive on ardroid. Love it so far. I'm just curious on what 
I need and need to do to have a higher flush percentage at harvest. Ive 
flushed - topped off the tank on numerous grows but I still can't seem to 
figure it out.
replyContent:
Finer flushing point, can have about 600ppm (or less) while flushing if desired
Don‚Äôt feed or drastically underfeed, so plant uses up energy stored in leaves, leaves will yellow and die - you seek to harvest when drained of excess but not dead
Aim, for 10 days of just water, cut at 7 to 14 depending on plant health, letting it weaken but not die
